{"tid":645570,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【減價情報】8GB RAM 頂配！小米 MIX2 Unibody 限時勁減一千, 旺角新地鋪5 月4日開張","createTime":"2018-04-28T09:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T02:09:29.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a3b6f9f7c0455125a8386a5b14f3e0ad7f0311","tid":645570,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/170508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F170508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cd8ba044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/170514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F170514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5776f6a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/170533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F170533_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3b810099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「小米 MIX 2S 五月初開賣」，睇到呢個消息，又會唔會有網友同小編一樣想知，舊 MIX 2 幾時減價呢？<br />\n<br />\n原來唔使等好耐，因為小米會係 MIX 2S 開賣當日同時推出限時優惠，當日於小米旺角新地鋪購買 MIX 2 Unibody、也就是 8GB RAM 版的話，可享 $1000 折扣優惠、以 $4499 購買。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\nMIX 2 Unibody 即減一千真係抵？<br />\n <br />\n但究竟呢個優惠又是否真係咁抵呢？<br />\n<br />\n小編翻查小米官網，發現小米 MIX 2 Unibody 現時售價其實係 $5099，換言之實際減價只有 $600。雖然減價後性價比仍算不錯，但考慮到新版 MIX 2S 同日開賣，有 S845 以及升級版雙鏡，似乎點都係買新機更著數喎！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▲ 小米旺角地鋪位於創興廣場地下，佔地 3,600 餘呎，將於5月4日10:00開業，網傳月租150萬<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▲ 小米旺角地鋪開幕日會有限時優惠，包括小米MIX 2 Unibody 減 $1,000 / 米家IH電飯煲減 $100 / 小米空氣淨化器2S 減 $150 / 米家行車記錄儀減 $200 等"},{"pid":"2b05228bdc0134df153d317d29dacfeb400cf6d7","tid":645570,"uid":77492,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"e8e2481c4fa026133099d337142355b2c2093b99","tid":645570,"uid":281,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a28760c0269453758a04db5b268b22e7e7a9f0b","tid":645570,"uid":152589,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"咁貴不如買iPhone"},{"pid":"f99a3dca696b60343e26f56a1cbb10fa6f80524b","tid":645570,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"小米七千個黑名單連結曝光！版主即試，香港小米手機有無中伏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/645601/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/645601/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58e7f5107762265e4479d9c6cb50548d3b97e368","tid":645570,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"網上傳出一個小米 API 連結資料，內容是關於小米手機自動封殺一系列連結的黑名單。點解被封鎖？係唔係因為內容不當，滿是暴力、色情資訊，所以被封鎖？唔係！ 被封鎖的原因，十有八九是同政治掛勾。如果網友係用緊小米手機，上網係咪真係會因而受到限制，睇唔到小米唔俾你睇到的內容？版主即刻試俾你睇，香港小米手機有無中伏！<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的連結中，可以看到有不少重要信息：miui、api，一睇就好明顯係同小米有關；browser，即係關係到小米瀏覽器事；blackurl，仲唔係小米針對網站的黑名單？版主 search 過，總共約有 7 千多個連結被小米瀏覽器封殺，不過並不是整個網站被封，只是指定的「敏感」文章，才會被封鎖。版主利用 chrome 瀏覽器打開這些被封殺網站，發現大部份的連結，都是同政治有關"},{"pid":"90e7a7d99c3ace5a203bf44d65e8fe073037b2f1","tid":645570,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:21:41.000Z","msg":"用an做政治人物都是反智的行為"},{"pid":"0d4f6bc52e5fe1433cba77d2d0ab07077d4867dc","tid":645570,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1682fc6577f96bd438225ad441c3b3bfdb73167","tid":645570,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58e7f5107762265e4479d9c6cb50548d3b97e368","tid":645570,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:40:04.000Z","msg